EARTH Return Of The Lord Of Magic

NATURAL PRINCIPLES OF LIFE Magicians, Hermonians, People Vol II EARTH Return Of The Lord Of Magic

Astilus, son of the Great Mage Merlin, the Last Lord of Magic – after the annihilation of mankind on the Seventh Planet of the Keron system, came to Earth. With the help of the ancient race of Hermonian, the mage began building a squad of superheroes who would be willing to sacrifice their lives to defend humanity. In the future they will be referred to as: The Oak Table Covenant.

The stories of Volume II combine the earthly present with the trends of fantasy and science fiction. The magic and technology of the Humble Bell ship for intergalactic travel will collide with earthly technology and human programming thought.

The ancient elements will unexpectedly merge with the actions of hackers. The will to be immortal will collide with the love of ordinary people, and their feelings will face a deadly threat.

Beliefs, diversity, technology and nature in all its glory. I will take you right there, to the most ancient antiquity and the present present, and the world of magic will stand against hacking information systems.
